Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------PREV-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次作战的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回月面上遗留的原联邦基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.04,0:00:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月神基地曾经是联邦在月面的一大据点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在联邦主力被大量遣往地球支援的间隙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不慎落入敌手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决定将夺回月神基地的作战计划付诸实施
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会帮我 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达AGE-FX 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量敌人机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正降落基地周边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有这样的大部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的驻守兵力足以应付
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.75,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你本可以躲起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.32,0:01:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入近距离防御系统火力范围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在这里做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我瞧瞧 你的真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的了 高达
