Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人机动战士 进入有效射程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始射击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打下那些苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预定地点着陆后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即搭建推进阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法德中队 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是德文中队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30秒后降落月面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里来的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说有埋伏？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月面上的话 掉下去应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种战斗方式 你打算持续到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家总有一天会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望你来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这是这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球一定比这里还美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记里写的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX 正在敌人防线形成突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法德中队要求炮击支援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围有友军吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预定炮击坐标上无友军部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1分钟后 开始逐次炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 通知下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后续部队跟上得太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 催促艾伦格雷亚斯加快动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊萨上士 呼叫阿马迪厄斯号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统 侦测到不明舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据库匹配…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚修船长的海盗船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是巴洛诺克号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 来凑个热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样会妨碍作战进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即给我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我无法从命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不听命于他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防线失守…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又以新的姿态出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来机师是个强力X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我去迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就想会一会高达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否给我这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击败他的人必须是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想看到功劳被地球联邦军的降将夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在劝你专注于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这次还看您的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久战不胜的话 我可能会按捺不住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨 到时你自可前来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预感？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您现在还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为还没有 完成对我的考察？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像了解你哥哥多勒·普洛斯特一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 也理解你潜伏的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向自己发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果是个拿部下生命当儿戏的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会亲手要了你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为了哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能报上这次作战中阵亡将士的姓名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山姆·格里芬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林·芬斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 格拉德·奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是些性情中人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但论技术无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝你记住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些 本舰的损失如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有许多士兵受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是 时刻牵挂着部下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是并肩作战的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想忘记也难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死者们的灵魂始终活在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知我可能取你性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么留我在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能者居其位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有我需要的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是贝森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人炮火猛烈 无法继续推进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在请求火力支援
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是赞塔3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞塔2中弹 请求…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久攻不下的话 损失会越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须尽早让这种战斗结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来进展还顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻陷只是时间问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可难说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘对这种状况应该早有准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太可能轻易败退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能有什么变数吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说 还不能太过乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里吧 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是能量核心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 听我指示找到起爆点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到还会有合作的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面可不会那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把X限制器的输出调到最大？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不知会对身体造成多大负担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就用我的身体采集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了对抗那台高达 锥炮需要越多越好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要战斗力 我可以协助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:13:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会驾驶冯法尔西娅出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下作为机师虽然经验尚浅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但作为X-Rounder的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定能祝您一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果觉得我在拖累您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽管弃我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 随我来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在能够理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多勒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我信了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然背负着无数人的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 为他出力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉卡 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆·纳拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冯法尔西娅 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死 步枪的能量不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光躲的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人由我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新型机？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我击落高达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您见识下我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是芙拉姆·纳拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟如此善战…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 敌军已经入侵到这种地方来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该可以和解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗 别再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个机师 在说什么胡话？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.95,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还有脸说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止争斗 让我们好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同为人类的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道在这漫长的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死去了多少人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和解已经是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便为了让那些人的牺牲不白费
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也必须停止战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些死去的人们不可能瞑目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被对方的气势压倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的找到了自己的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就相信自己直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信…自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二对一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让她和同伴汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 既然再次出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定做好心理准备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为维甘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须葬身此地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:21:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道伊泽尔坎特真正的目的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫嚣的伊甸计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非维甘的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子从伊泽尔坎特本人那里得知了真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 地球种怎能理解伊泽尔坎特大人的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只为伊泽尔坎特大人而战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须听你的疯言疯语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人机动战士部队接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认敌人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散开 全队散开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击？月神基地来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来轮到我出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉拉德·斯普里根 出阵
